    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全新版本 S2.4 夺宝奇谋 现已上线！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深渊是一个为好斗者、寻宝猎人、探险家而生的流放之地，如果你信奉着“高风险高回报”的教条，那么我相信你能够在这里捞的“盆满钵满”！记住，只有活着离开深渊，才有一切后续！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你好运，指挥官！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于此游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无烬战争是一款俯视角PVP夺宝撤离MMO。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一个漂泊于各大星系的指挥官，为了争夺生存与资源反复深入危险重重的深渊，探索并争夺各种宝物，当然这里那些凶恶的“原住民”应该不会欢迎你的到来，但比他们更加可怕的是潜伏的“人心”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活着撤离，交易战利品并不断提升自我！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/dc055d290fef81bc85d84bffa905476a.poster.avif?t=1771989338\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/dc055d290fef81bc85d84bffa905476a.webm?t=1771989338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/dc055d290fef81bc85d84bffa905476a.mp4?t=1771989338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MMO+搜打撤：屏住呼吸，拿到就撤！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>高风险高回报：</strong>每一步都是一场博弈，在装备搭配、搜刮路线、战术策略中均有无数次豪赌！记住只有成功撤出才有收益，死亡即为前功尽弃！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>未知与刺激：</strong>迷雾笼罩深渊，敌友难辨，危机四伏——每一次探宝，都有无限的随机性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多层级地图选择：</strong>无论你是猛攻突袭亦或潜行摸金，总有属于你的一块战场。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/26d1ea46b9e6c457f3ca7fcb7c49a540.poster.avif?t=1771989338\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/26d1ea46b9e6c457f3ca7fcb7c49a540.webm?t=1771989338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/26d1ea46b9e6c457f3ca7fcb7c49a540.mp4?t=1771989338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1个人的秀场、1队人的战场</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无限Build组合：</strong>招募40多名独特漂流者、自由搭配共12个系列的百余种装备，和数十种战术道具，创造专属战斗流派。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拼操作，就是干：</strong>技能、地形、走位均有可能成为你制胜的关键，拿出你的实力激情火拼！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/31348938e6b7d5a12cb1375344dbc3cf.poster.avif?t=1771989338\" width=616 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/31348938e6b7d5a12cb1375344dbc3cf.webm?t=1771989338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/31348938e6b7d5a12cb1375344dbc3cf.mp4?t=1771989338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>搜刮物资并武装到牙齿</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自由交易：</strong>全球互通交易行，你带出来的东西都能换成奇珍异宝。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一次撤离均是成长：</strong>丰富多元的科技树系统，让带出来的宝贝全都能变成战力！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3142050/extras/fa0165b46c8f5a9da0e580b0934d4126.poster.avif?t=1771989338